Goosepump happens when the poetry of National Poet of Pakistan and Poet of East Dr. Muhammad Allama Iqbal gets together with the sound of tha Nation i.e Coke Studio. Tears tears. I remember I read this kalaam in school and it is something that is cemented on the inner wall of my heart. 
Ki Muhammad S.A.W se wafa tu ne to hum tere hain.
Yeh jahan cheez hai kia loh o qalam tere hain. 

Something I think that these two lines of Iqbal are greater than anything which any writer has ever written in the universe.
